{/* Product Details & Key Features Section */}

Key Features

Predictive Analytics: We predict COPD exacerbations and hypertension spikes uts to provide timely risk alerts and actionable insights. Emergency Alerts: Our device continuously monitors your vital signs and instantly alerts emergency contacts and hospitals in case of a serious issue. Personalized Care Plans: AI-powered real-time health reports help doctors make precise diagnoses and tailored treatments. Real-Time Monitoring: Tracks heart rate, SpO2 levels, and other vitals to provide health updates for proactive care. AI-Based Risk Detection: Uses AI to analyze biological data and detect potential health risks early. LED Severity Indicator: Integrated LED strip displays health risk levels with three severity modes for instant awareness. Dual Battery System: Two batteries allow continuous 24/7 use—one charges while the other powers the device. Sensors & Modules: PPG, ECG, SpO2 sensor, skin temperature, accelerometer, gyroscope, and skin conductance sensors. Processor & Power: ESP32-S3 with BLE 5.0, 2 rechargeable 300-500mAh Li-ion batteries, and waterproof plastic/metal housing.
{/* Pricing Section */}
